                            <comment id="12802305" author="jbellis" created="Tue, 19 Jan 2010 15:41:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;until this is fixed, running nodeprobe cleanup on each live node &amp;amp; restarting it should fix this (by removing undelivered hints forcibly).  depending on your replication factor you may have hints that are not removed by cleanup; in that case you can remove the hint files from data/system/&lt;b&gt;Hint&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
